Happy Birthday to meeee! I can finally say I am in a happy place in life. I am full of love, blessings and joy! I feel like I’m only now learning to be comfortable with stepping in to my voice and power; and  the best is yet to come!🤩 It only took me being 32! Lol no matter where we’re at in life the best we can do is enjoy this roller coaster, play the cards we are given and learn to dance in the rain!☔️💃🏼✨ SENDING YOU ALL SO MUCH LOVE!💖🌈✨

I WON SOMETHING!🎖️✨
Yesterday I was named one of the Visalia Pride 2023 Grand Marshals🤩 This meant so much to me and made me see that everything I do through community outreach and through drag doesn’t go unnoticed. @thesourcelgbt came in at a time when I was desperate for community and acceptance. After I found myself, my main motivation was reaching out and connecting with the other Johnny’s, Millenia’s and Neuro-spicies of the world who are in need of a caring and helping hand.🫂This is the most important award I’ve ever received and I’m happy to be able to say that I’m grateful and fortunate to finally be living my best life✨ Love y’all, and thank you The Source💖
.
